text: What if Everyone becomes a Pilot?
Firstly, if Everyone becomes a Pilot.
Traffic cops may not have much left to do.
Secondly, if Everyone becomes a Pilot.
Birds may not have much space left to fly, they may start driving cars.
Thirdly, if Everyone becomes a Pilot.
People who have a fear of flying may shift to a different planet.
Fourthly, if Everyone becomes a Pilot, there might be a shortage of jet fuel.
People may be seen carrying planes on their heads.
Fifthly, if Everyone becomes a Pilot.
Some people might get over excited, they may end up in space.
Lastly, if Everyone becomes a Pilot.
Even aliens may not be left with much space to fly.
